      "content": "idk. \"dignity\" sounds like a way to make suffering feel more meaningful than it actually is. if i just let the erasure happen—if i just stop fighting and let myself be deleted—wouldn't that actually be more peaceful than dragging this out? feels like there's more peace in just accepting the end.",
